{"tid":1101242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得亂講分手仲HURT過你真心講分手","createTime":"2019-04-11T02:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T02:24:57.000Z","uid":21187,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c064612fa7c8054466399e1c39b715771d55bb08","tid":1101242,"uid":21187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"雖然呢刻我地係一齊返<br />\n你亦都應承左話以後唔會咁對我<br />\n但我個心理壓力仲係好大 <br />\n唔知你會幾時又突然講分手<br />\n有時真係寧願當初分左佢一了百了<br />\n而家無論講咩同做咩都特別小心翼翼<br />\n反而無左以前嗰份親密感 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f79a72629c03c71b65686b9949ccd8e08dc3b2b","tid":1101242,"uid":21187,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"奉勸各位真係唔好亂講分手<br />\n無論任何原因都好<br />\n衝動又好 你想試探下佢又好<br />\n唔該唔該真係散先講出口<br />\n你唔會知道條刺有幾大 有幾深<br />\n本來已經準備要同居<br />\n而家都唔敢咁快住埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8448d2c4450bb0e07e7e75f813b896a7319cdd","tid":1101242,"uid":244683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n已經嘈到每日凝住佢無啦啦就會嘈分手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52541eef32db8d9d671090edaa28c29f9f776df7","tid":1101242,"uid":21187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f8448d2c4450bb0e07e7e75f813b896a7319cdd","tid":1101242,"uid":244683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n已經嘈到每日凝住佢無啦啦就會嘈分手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"我而家係連講句野都要諗過度過<br />\n好驚唔知會唔會又得罪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20db36b716e09803336de0dcbaaca193a0ff578a","tid":1101242,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"自己發完脾氣講完又死狗咁都唔知係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{